132efcb19ee9d4cd4608f9e41a097ab292e7314b5589708a4398f81d727ad17b541047143d3f77628c5e1d70c404b4164625f81aa65a0bcdf6a76611ef09d74e  0001-Add-uacess-to-udev.patch
"
